::Hot Rod::

He heard her say "heads up".
"What?!" He turned to her, and was surprized by the part, coming at his
face. He grabbed it, only to drop, grab, drop, and grab.
"Oh you think thats funny do yo?" He put the part down, picked up a
lazer torch, and tossed it to her.
"Watch out, hon."
